### Create a new order
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### Create an order without username (anonymous order)
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": null,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 3
    }
  ]
}

### Get all orders
GET http://localhost:8080/orders
Accept: application/json

### Get order by ID (replace {id} with an actual ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/1
Accept: application/json

### Get orders by user ID (replace {userId} with an actual user ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/user/1
Accept: application/json

### Get order items by order ID (replace {orderId} with an actual order ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/1/items
Accept: application/json